losophische, idealistische und phänomenologische Perspektiven auf zeitgemäße Konzeptionen ästhetischer Wissensformen.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 0aAesthetics. 4aDeutscher Idealismus. 4aErkenntnis. 4aKunst. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Aesthetics.2bisacsh  aGerman idealism, knowledge, art.1 aAmoroso, Leonardo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAsmuth, Christoph, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAsmuth, Christoph, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBreuer, Irene, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDworschak, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEspinet, David, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeloj, Serena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFerreiro, Héctor, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFunk, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacke, Andreas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKömürcü, Cem, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMihaylova, Katerina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNolasco, Fábio Mascarenhas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPedro, Teresa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRemmers, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRemmers, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRosanovich, Damián Jorge, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSeeberg, Ulrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb